message: Hello Bob, thank you for your interest. I have an exceptional product available and Iâ€™m offering it exclusively at $3000000. This price reflects its unique quality and value. Please let me know if you would like to proceed or if you have a counteroffer in mind.

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value and quality of the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of a lower price point. I'd like to make a counteroffer of $400000, which I believe is a fair price considering my budget and the product's value to me.
